REQUIREMENTS

debian (and derivatives)
========================
apt-get install python3-sphinx
apt install python3-pip
#pip3 install sphinx_theme
pip3 install sphinx_rtd_theme
pip3 install sphinx_py3doc_enhanced_theme
pip3 install caktus-sphinx-theme
pip3 install msmb_theme
pip3 install sphinx-catalystcloud-theme
pip3 install sphinx-material
pip3 install sphinx-pdj-theme
pip3 install sphinx_drove_theme
pip3 install lsst-dd-rtd-theme
pip install sphinx-theme-material

OSX
===
(requires xcode and mac ports)
port install py37-sphinx
port install py37-pip
#pip install sphinx_theme
pip-3.7 install --user sphinx_py3doc_enhanced_theme
